-- MOVES-F&C names Howard Pearce as chair of new advisory council
-- 
-- Thu Oct 16, 2014 06:04AM EDT
-- None



Oct 16 (Reuters) - F&C Investments (F&C), a part of BMO Financial Group's <BMO.TO> BMO Global Asset Management, said it appointed Howard Pearce as chair of its new responsible investment advisory council.

Pearce will begin work at the company immediately but will take up his role officially on Jan. 1, the asset manager said in a statement.